  "title": "Cloud Infra Engineer/Senior [Kubernetes Exp / Cert]",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan, execute, monitor, and control all technical aspects of projects.</li>\n  <li>Lead or contribute to new system/network infrastructure setups or upgrades.</li>\n  <li>Support operational systems in line with contractual Service Level Agreements (SLAs).</li>\n  <li>Conduct routine preventive maintenance and manage operational activities efficiently.</li>\n  <li>Prepare comprehensive project documentation and reports.</li>\n  <li>Troubleshoot and resolve technical issues promptly.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of Windows Server OS and Linux OS; experience in virtualized environments is a plus.</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience with virtualization, hypervisors, and the Nutanix platform is an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Understanding of VPNs and firewall appliances is beneficial.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with network switches and routers is preferred.</li>\n  <li>Excellent written and verbal communication skills to articulate technical concepts to both technical and non-technical stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Proactive, dynamic, and analytical with strong conceptual thinking abilities.</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and collaboratively, with strong interpersonal skills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Work Location:</strong> North / Central</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>kayla@talentsis.com.sg </strong>for immediate processing.</p>\n<p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
